Class Donor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davis.Donor

  • public class Donor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to represent a Donor in memory. It contains methods that check the validity of emails as well as methods to create a donor object from a file.
    Author:
    Samuel Kyle Davis
